		<title>投资就是一种收藏</title>
		<link>https://laputancn.wordpress.com/2008/02/16/%e6%8a%95%e8%b5%84%e5%b0%b1%e6%98%af%e4%b8%80%e7%a7%8d%e6%94%b6%e8%97%8f/</link>
